 R(x)=\sum_{p\leq x}\frac{\ln p}p-\ln x 
 \int_0^x\frac{tR'(t)}{\ln t}dt 
 \frac{xR(x)}{\ln x}-\int_0^x\sum_{p\leq t}\frac{\ln p}p\left(\frac1{\ln t}-\frac1{\ln^2 t}\right)dt+x-\text{li}(x) 
